To use Vibify:
1. Download and run the app.
2. Get your Spotify Client ID and Secret:
   - Go to https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard/
   - Create an app (e.g., "Vibify").
   - Copy Client ID and Client Secret.
   - Set Redirect URI to http://localhost:8888 in your app settings.
3. Enter these when prompted by the app.
4. Enjoy!
